<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4930681>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Cigclisula turrita (Smitt, 1873). A–D, MCZ # 92, syntype, Florida. A, part of encrusting colony. B, primary orifice. C, group of ovicelled zooids and elliptical frontal avicularia. D, ovicelled zooid and elliptical frontal avicularia. Scale bars: A, B = 400 µm; C = 40 µm; D = 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4930681/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

